					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think Blargg was the one that tested this and figured out where the missing do is(n't), and he's usually correct about this stuff. It might not be possible to figure the exact cycle in software, but after aligning the PPU and CPU as much as possible and enabling rendering at different times you can have an idea of the latest this can be done that will still cause the dot to be skipped. Just by looking at the picture you can tell if it's being skipped or not.</div>

